1
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:34,520
=Lady Liberty=

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,980
=Episode 15=

3
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:44,900
So?

4
00:01:46,044 --> 00:01:47,488
Think it through carefully.

5
00:01:52,220 --> 00:01:52,660
Mr. Fan,

6
00:01:53,180 --> 00:01:54,260
give me a straight answer.

7
00:01:55,300 --> 00:01:56,420
How much of this

8
00:01:56,900 --> 00:01:58,820
is based on Chenxing's
value in your eyes,

9
00:02:00,140 --> 00:02:01,620
and how much is because of He Han?

10
00:02:02,420 --> 00:02:04,660
Of course, it's because of Chenxing.

11
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:06,060
I am investing in Chenxing.

12
00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:08,820
What I value is Chenxing's future.

13
00:02:10,300 --> 00:02:11,780
Then, what if

14
00:02:12,111 --> 00:02:13,444
He Han is not part of that future?

15
00:02:15,660 --> 00:02:16,900
Weren't you just...

16
00:02:22,540 --> 00:02:23,620
It's such a pity

17
00:02:23,620 --> 00:02:24,780
that you are not together.

18
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:27,140
Right now, He Han
is a freelance creator.

19
00:02:27,140 --> 00:02:28,900
He is not tied to any company.

20
00:02:29,380 --> 00:02:30,444
Doesn't it mean

21
00:02:30,866 --> 00:02:32,860
that he is just
waiting to return to Chenxing?

22
00:02:33,140 --> 00:02:33,820
He Han and I

23
00:02:33,820 --> 00:02:35,933
are just old friends who
look out for each other.

24
00:02:37,220 --> 00:02:38,660
I hope those who invest in Chenxing

25
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:41,500
value Chenxing and me,

26
00:02:41,933 --> 00:02:43,600
not a bundled deal with He Han.

27
00:02:44,644 --> 00:02:45,511
I understand.

28
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:46,980
I understand.

29
00:02:47,980 --> 00:02:48,700
I know

30
00:02:49,060 --> 00:02:50,140
you have integrity.

31
00:02:51,260 --> 00:02:51,820
As for me,

32
00:02:52,540 --> 00:02:54,060
what I value is you

33
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:55,940
and your Chenxing.

34
00:02:56,340 --> 00:02:57,220
As for He Han,

35
00:02:57,740 --> 00:02:59,980
he is just an added bonus.

36
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:01,666
How do you prove that?

37
00:03:01,700 --> 00:03:02,460
In business,

38
00:03:02,860 --> 00:03:04,060
money is proof.

39
00:03:05,133 --> 00:03:06,688
I won't change the number here.

40
00:03:07,377 --> 00:03:09,000
That should be proof enough, right?

41
00:03:12,488 --> 00:03:14,755
Remove the parts related
to He Han in the contract.

42
00:03:15,100 --> 00:03:16,355
We can talk another time.

43
00:03:20,740 --> 00:03:21,660
No need.

44
00:03:23,660 --> 00:03:24,660
We can do it now.

45
00:03:27,020 --> 00:03:28,140
I have prepared

46
00:03:28,340 --> 00:03:29,300
both options.

47
00:03:29,820 --> 00:03:31,330
You can take them back and review them.

48
00:03:31,355 --> 00:03:32,044
That is fine.

49
00:03:32,155 --> 00:03:33,666
Then, over the next couple of days,

50
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:35,740
let's get it signed as
soon as possible, alright?

51
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:38,100
I may not be that fast.

52
00:03:38,340 --> 00:03:39,700
The sooner, the better.

53
00:03:44,820 --> 00:03:45,620
I need to go in now.

54
00:04:33,622 --> 00:04:34,420
Instant noodles?

55
00:04:34,444 --> 00:04:35,260
Careful. It's hot.

56
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:43,460
Hey,

57
00:04:43,860 --> 00:04:44,980
where are you working now?

58
00:04:45,422 --> 00:04:46,660
This is your alt account, right?

59
00:04:46,940 --> 00:04:47,260
Bro,

60
00:04:47,820 --> 00:04:48,540
join our guild.

61
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,422
Let's play together.

62
00:04:58,980 --> 00:04:59,666
Come here.

63
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:00,660
What?

64
00:05:00,660 --> 00:05:01,380
I said come here.

65
00:05:11,022 --> 00:05:13,133
So Lin Zhanqiao still
ended up pushing you around.

66
00:05:13,140 --> 00:05:13,700
What happened?

67
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:15,511
Got new people and stopped valuing you?

68
00:05:16,820 --> 00:05:17,620
To be fair,

69
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:19,780
you do look quite sharp now.

70
00:05:20,020 --> 00:05:21,340
That's you, darn it.

71
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:24,450
Watch your words, Mr. Gu Yan.

72
00:05:24,450 --> 00:05:25,900
Don't be sarcastic or snide here.

73
00:05:26,780 --> 00:05:28,260
No, you just want to dress like this,

74
00:05:28,420 --> 00:05:30,177
but don't want to be judged and ranked.

75
00:05:30,266 --> 00:05:32,030
But let me tell you,
once you dress like this,

76
00:05:32,044 --> 00:05:33,377
you will be judged and ranked.

77
00:05:33,644 --> 00:05:35,288
Because you are already in that system.

78
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,377
It feels uncomfortable to wear,

79
00:05:38,911 --> 00:05:39,733
so I won't wear it.

80
00:05:42,244 --> 00:05:44,133
If it's uncomfortable,
then just don't wear it.

81
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:49,540
That is right.

82
00:05:50,555 --> 00:05:51,555
I won't wear it.

83
00:06:01,977 --> 00:06:03,022
You are really cutting it?

84
00:06:04,860 --> 00:06:05,660
With this one snip,

85
00:06:06,022 --> 00:06:06,980
a thousand is gone.

86
00:06:09,711 --> 00:06:10,888
Would he not feel the loss?

87
00:06:11,180 --> 00:06:12,200
Help me cut it, too.

88
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:13,420
You said it.

89
00:06:13,980 --> 00:06:14,740
No compensation.

90
00:06:14,740 --> 00:06:15,180
Cut it.

91
00:06:15,180 --> 00:06:16,140
But we are not paying for it.

92
00:06:16,140 --> 00:06:16,620
Cut it.

93
00:06:17,020 --> 00:06:17,540
You said it.

94
00:06:17,860 --> 00:06:18,780
This feels great. I...

95
00:06:19,111 --> 00:06:20,666
These scissors are sharp. Just cut it.

96
00:06:22,311 --> 00:06:23,580
If you keep cutting like this,

97
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:25,100
will he not make you pay for it?

98
00:06:59,900 --> 00:07:00,860
Gu Yan's award.

99
00:07:01,355 --> 00:07:03,133
He is not here, and neither are you,

100
00:07:03,244 --> 00:07:04,620
so I accepted it on your behalf.

101
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:10,940
So?

102
00:07:11,580 --> 00:07:12,100
All settled?

103
00:07:15,340 --> 00:07:16,180
I got Mr. Fan,

104
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:17,820
but I lost Gu Yan.

105
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:19,340
That won't happen.

106
00:07:19,866 --> 00:07:21,580
He is just throwing a bit of a tantrum.

107
00:07:21,580 --> 00:07:22,650
He is easy to calm down.

108
00:07:22,650 --> 00:07:24,300
Just explain things clearly to him.

109
00:07:27,300 --> 00:07:28,900
Think back to when the two of us

110
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:33,700
decided to build Chenxing together.

111
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:36,660
Up until now,

112
00:07:37,355 --> 00:07:38,933
it has only been five or six years.

113
00:07:43,660 --> 00:07:45,260
If I sign this paper,

114
00:07:46,733 --> 00:07:47,977
it will all be over.

115
00:07:54,900 --> 00:07:56,620
Mr. Fan takes 70 percent,

116
00:07:58,260 --> 00:07:59,620
and I keep 30 percent.

117
00:08:01,980 --> 00:08:03,660
I may become an employee,

118
00:08:04,460 --> 00:08:05,200
but at least,

119
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:09,060
Chenxing's name will still be there.

120
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:11,140
That makes me feel a little better.

121
00:08:16,100 --> 00:08:17,500
No matter what,

122
00:08:18,688 --> 00:08:21,333
it's still better than losing
the whole company, right?

123
00:08:31,644 --> 00:08:32,933
If you don't want to sell it,

124
00:08:34,020 --> 00:08:35,022
then don't sell it.

125
00:08:35,300 --> 00:08:36,980
There will always be
a way to keep going.

126
00:08:39,180 --> 00:08:39,900
Who are you?

127
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:42,860
You are Lin Zhanqiao. Come on.

128
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:47,100
Listen,

129
00:08:48,820 --> 00:08:50,620
smash this trophy right now.

130
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:51,580
Let it all out.

131
00:08:53,500 --> 00:08:54,660
Smash it. Smash it hard.

132
00:08:54,740 --> 00:08:56,980
Just like you smashed
our trophy back then.

133
00:08:56,980 --> 00:08:57,820
Smash it hard.

134
00:09:01,700 --> 00:09:03,420
I didn't do that on purpose back then.

135
00:09:03,820 --> 00:09:05,140
Then, do it on purpose now.

136
00:09:06,020 --> 00:09:07,644
Is your broken trophy still around?

137
00:09:07,940 --> 00:09:08,500
Of course.

138
00:09:10,940 --> 00:09:12,620
Mr. Fan said he would get us a new one.

139
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:13,620
I said no.

140
00:09:14,300 --> 00:09:16,340
A trophy full of scars is a real trophy,

141
00:09:16,700 --> 00:09:17,420
right?

142
00:09:22,340 --> 00:09:23,020
Smash it.

143
00:09:23,111 --> 00:09:24,580
If you won't, I'll do it for you.

144
00:09:24,733 --> 00:09:26,540
Why are you so determined
to make me smash it?

145
00:09:26,540 --> 00:09:28,320
Then, I'll smash it.
If you won't, I'll.

146
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:30,311
Or are you afraid Gu Yan will get mad?

147
00:09:30,580 --> 00:09:31,460
Not at all.

148
00:09:32,620 --> 00:09:33,940
He is very emotionally stable.

149
00:09:34,140 --> 00:09:35,020
Calm and composed.

150
00:09:35,780 --> 00:09:38,244
At most, when he is upset,
he just leaves for a while.

151
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:39,580
At least, from now on,

152
00:09:39,580 --> 00:09:40,580
I won't have to worry

153
00:09:40,740 --> 00:09:41,860
that at any time, anywhere,

154
00:09:41,860 --> 00:09:44,100
I may have to go
clean up someone's mess.

155
00:09:50,700 --> 00:09:51,460
Are you saying that

156
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:53,580
because you miss me?

157
00:09:56,780 --> 00:09:57,180
Right?

158
00:09:57,420 --> 00:09:59,660
The show is over for today, okay?

159
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:01,780
Your acting was very obvious today.

160
00:10:01,940 --> 00:10:02,580
Was it?

161
00:10:02,580 --> 00:10:03,180
Of course.

162
00:10:03,422 --> 00:10:05,355
There was so much
applause from the audience.

163
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,660
That means I was right.

164
00:10:06,660 --> 00:10:09,020
That was because
I led the applause, okay?

165
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:09,940
You led the applause?

166
00:10:09,940 --> 00:10:10,260
Yes.

167
00:10:10,260 --> 00:10:12,140
Why didn't you
stand up and lead it for us?

168
00:10:12,580 --> 00:10:14,260
A few men beside you had fallen asleep.

169
00:10:18,580 --> 00:10:19,940
You should go back first.

170
00:10:20,260 --> 00:10:21,500
They have plans tonight.

171
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:23,111
I don't know when they will be back.

172
00:10:23,711 --> 00:10:24,755
I am not in a hurry.

173
00:10:24,911 --> 00:10:26,266
I have nowhere to go anyway.

174
00:10:28,740 --> 00:10:30,540
Don't you develop so many hotels?

175
00:10:30,622 --> 00:10:32,260
You are always pointing at some hotel

176
00:10:32,260 --> 00:10:33,210
and saying you built it,

177
00:10:33,222 --> 00:10:34,955
and they still owe you tens of millions.

178
00:10:35,420 --> 00:10:36,620
Why not find a hotel now,

179
00:10:36,820 --> 00:10:37,700
take a bath,

180
00:10:38,180 --> 00:10:39,540
drink some warm milk,

181
00:10:39,780 --> 00:10:41,140
and get a good sleep?

182
00:10:42,888 --> 00:10:44,377
I'll stay another half hour.

183
00:10:44,444 --> 00:10:46,377
Go on with your work.
I won't bother you.

184
00:10:49,180 --> 00:10:49,940
I think

185
00:10:50,380 --> 00:10:51,500
staying in this room

186
00:10:52,422 --> 00:10:53,660
feels especially comfortable.

187
00:10:54,380 --> 00:10:55,140
Do you know why?

188
00:10:56,420 --> 00:10:56,940
No.

189
00:10:57,900 --> 00:10:59,420
Because your boss

190
00:11:00,100 --> 00:11:01,940
has excellent taste in decor.

191
00:11:02,660 --> 00:11:04,260
You know how many people spend a fortune

192
00:11:04,260 --> 00:11:06,050
making their homes look like palaces,

193
00:11:06,050 --> 00:11:07,488
only for them to feel uncomfortable?

194
00:11:07,660 --> 00:11:09,220
That is just paying to suffer.

195
00:11:09,660 --> 00:11:10,380
Look at you,

196
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:13,340
and your boss's female friend, Zhou Mei.

197
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:15,100
Why do you both like living here?

198
00:11:15,260 --> 00:11:16,288
That makes sense.

199
00:11:17,088 --> 00:11:18,580
Are you talking to me about this

200
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:20,820
because you really
have no other girlfriends to ask out?

201
00:11:22,620 --> 00:11:24,340
Asking out other girlfriends right now

202
00:11:24,460 --> 00:11:25,460
would only upset me.

203
00:11:28,460 --> 00:11:29,780
What I need right now is peace.

204
00:11:32,860 --> 00:11:33,340
She's back.

205
00:11:35,260 --> 00:11:35,660
Ms. Lin.

206
00:11:36,340 --> 00:11:36,860
Ms. Lin.

207
00:11:37,820 --> 00:11:38,940
Ms. Lin...

208
00:11:39,622 --> 00:11:41,177
Qian Jingjing has been discharged.

209
00:11:41,340 --> 00:11:42,530
She is finally out.

210
00:11:42,530 --> 00:11:44,300
I don't plan to get
married anymore either.

211
00:11:44,860 --> 00:11:45,740
Before the wedding,

212
00:11:45,900 --> 00:11:47,244
being able to see a person clearly

213
00:11:47,420 --> 00:11:48,580
is heaven's arrangement.

214
00:11:49,666 --> 00:11:50,888
It's a good thing.

215
00:11:51,380 --> 00:11:52,660
Hasn't Zhangzhu always hoped

216
00:11:52,660 --> 00:11:53,990
you wouldn't get married again?

217
00:11:54,133 --> 00:11:56,270
As long as you have handled it
and thought it through.

218
00:11:56,380 --> 00:11:57,540
But he hasn't handled it.

219
00:11:58,140 --> 00:11:59,140
It's about the house.

220
00:11:59,420 --> 00:12:00,140
That house

221
00:12:00,140 --> 00:12:01,866
was originally
renovated for the wedding.

222
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:03,380
But since the wedding is off,

223
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:04,740
Qian Jingjing got so angry

224
00:12:04,740 --> 00:12:06,140
that she smashed the whole place.

225
00:12:07,488 --> 00:12:09,133
What do you mean by the whole place?

226
00:12:09,380 --> 00:12:11,100
She really smashed everything.

227
00:12:11,180 --> 00:12:12,311
Look at these photos.

228
00:12:14,660 --> 00:12:15,740
Everything is shattered.

229
00:12:17,460 --> 00:12:19,340
Wasn't Qian Jingjing's bone fractured?

230
00:12:19,700 --> 00:12:21,666
How could she still
smash things so badly?

231
00:12:22,260 --> 00:12:24,022
It's a house of 200-300 square meters.

232
00:12:24,620 --> 00:12:26,140
We must call the police. This is

233
00:12:26,260 --> 00:12:28,020
the destruction of
someone else's property.

234
00:12:28,020 --> 00:12:29,288
Once she is out of the hospital,

235
00:12:29,290 --> 00:12:30,800
she should spend
some time at the police station.

236
00:12:30,820 --> 00:12:31,500
Forget it.

237
00:12:32,140 --> 00:12:33,688
I build houses and do renovations.

238
00:12:33,690 --> 00:12:35,466
If it's smashed,
I'll just make a new one.

239
00:12:35,470 --> 00:12:37,044
The main thing is that no one gets hurt.

240
00:12:37,220 --> 00:12:38,500
Ms. Lin, I just think

241
00:12:38,700 --> 00:12:40,755
Zhangzhu will still be
staying here for a while.

242
00:12:41,100 --> 00:12:42,810
If... I mean,

243
00:12:42,810 --> 00:12:44,533
if Qian Jingjing comes here
to cause trouble

244
00:12:45,100 --> 00:12:47,340
and tries to smash your place,

245
00:12:48,060 --> 00:12:49,940
you must protect the people first.

246
00:12:50,044 --> 00:12:52,260
If anything gets broken,
I'll replace it for you.

247
00:12:53,540 --> 00:12:54,980
Until this matter is settled,

248
00:12:54,980 --> 00:12:56,850
I'll send people here
every day to stand guard.

249
00:12:57,244 --> 00:12:59,466
First, there is no need to
have someone on duty.

250
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:00,980
She probably won't hurt anyone.

251
00:13:01,260 --> 00:13:02,844
At most, she will just make a scene.

252
00:13:03,220 --> 00:13:04,940
Besides, you are here
to clean things up.

253
00:13:06,180 --> 00:13:06,540
Second,

254
00:13:07,180 --> 00:13:08,900
she probably won't go after Zhangzhu.

255
00:13:09,022 --> 00:13:10,940
After all,
the reason you called off the wedding

256
00:13:10,940 --> 00:13:11,980
has nothing to do with her.

257
00:13:13,940 --> 00:13:15,940
Ms. Lin, you really see things clearly.

258
00:13:16,820 --> 00:13:18,300
You are the most insightful

259
00:13:18,420 --> 00:13:19,260
and composed woman

260
00:13:19,500 --> 00:13:20,580
I have ever met.

261
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:21,340
For example...

262
00:13:21,980 --> 00:13:23,140
Where are you staying tonight?

263
00:13:25,660 --> 00:13:26,420
There are already

264
00:13:27,220 --> 00:13:28,580
three women here.

265
00:13:28,740 --> 00:13:30,380
It's not convenient
for me to stay, right?

266
00:13:30,740 --> 00:13:32,020
I was not asking you to stay here.

267
00:13:32,088 --> 00:13:34,450
What I mean is, you don't have to
go back to your place either.

268
00:13:34,460 --> 00:13:35,777
It has already been smashed anyway.

269
00:13:38,740 --> 00:13:39,260
Well,

270
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:41,860
alright then.

271
00:13:41,860 --> 00:13:42,660
I'll just

272
00:13:43,340 --> 00:13:44,420
find somewhere else to stay.

273
00:13:44,540 --> 00:13:45,220
That is easy.

274
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:48,140
After this is settled,

275
00:13:48,260 --> 00:13:49,940
I'll fix up your place properly.

276
00:13:51,300 --> 00:13:53,660
And I'll thank
your female friend as well.

277
00:13:54,180 --> 00:13:55,140
I'll get going, then.

278
00:13:56,300 --> 00:13:56,700
Alright.

279
00:14:05,580 --> 00:14:06,100
I am leaving.

280
00:14:12,950 --> 00:14:14,688
Now that your dad
is not getting married,

281
00:14:14,733 --> 00:14:16,111
shouldn't you celebrate?

282
00:14:16,311 --> 00:14:18,511
Once this one is gone,
another one comes right after.

283
00:14:22,380 --> 00:14:23,844
My dad is actually a good person.

284
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:26,060
He just keeps falling
for the wrong women.

285
00:14:26,060 --> 00:14:27,511
What kind of problem is that?

286
00:14:28,111 --> 00:14:29,340
If you say he is love-obsessed,

287
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:31,180
he can immediately fall for someone else

288
00:14:31,340 --> 00:14:32,733
and chase after her like crazy.

289
00:14:33,660 --> 00:14:34,820
It has left me with a shadow.

290
00:14:34,955 --> 00:14:36,780
Whenever a man pursues me,
I think of my dad,

291
00:14:36,940 --> 00:14:38,200
and I feel it's ridiculous.

292
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:41,460
So now,

293
00:14:41,888 --> 00:14:43,380
I am always the one pursuing men.

294
00:14:44,420 --> 00:14:47,220
And the colder a man is toward me,

295
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:48,100
the more I feel

296
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:50,140
it's strangely addictive.

297
00:14:51,740 --> 00:14:53,100
Like someone like Mr. He Han.

298
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:56,340
How is He Han cold toward you?

299
00:14:56,340 --> 00:14:57,620
Isn't he quite warm with you?

300
00:14:57,900 --> 00:14:58,860
No.

301
00:14:59,220 --> 00:15:01,620
He is only enthusiastic
when talking about you,

302
00:15:01,620 --> 00:15:02,740
not about me.

303
00:15:04,420 --> 00:15:06,100
But I am still happy.

304
00:15:08,060 --> 00:15:09,100
As long as I can see him,

305
00:15:09,100 --> 00:15:10,220
I feel happy.

306
00:15:11,620 --> 00:15:13,060
Were you the one chasing him before?

307
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:13,980
No.

308
00:15:14,260 --> 00:15:15,088
So, he chased you?

309
00:15:15,620 --> 00:15:16,380
Not really.

310
00:15:17,020 --> 00:15:18,644
Then, how did you two get together?

311
00:15:20,900 --> 00:15:21,620
We argued.

312
00:15:22,420 --> 00:15:23,780
We argued our way into it.

313
00:15:24,222 --> 00:15:25,260
What kind of arguments?

314
00:15:25,260 --> 00:15:25,620
Were they

315
00:15:26,540 --> 00:15:28,220
playful arguments or real fights?

316
00:15:29,260 --> 00:15:29,740
Real fights.

317
00:15:31,311 --> 00:15:32,933
The kind that could blow the place up.

318
00:15:32,977 --> 00:15:34,622
How did you make up after fighting?

319
00:15:35,777 --> 00:15:37,288
Zhou Mei hasn't come back yet.

320
00:15:37,466 --> 00:15:39,311
She asked me to
leave the door open for her.

321
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:41,060
So, how did you make up?

322
00:15:44,660 --> 00:15:45,060
I forgot.

323
00:16:03,060 --> 00:16:07,900
(Three Years Ago)

324
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:10,380
♪If the sky and the sea
turned upside down♪

325
00:16:10,380 --> 00:16:10,860
Thanks.

326
00:16:15,577 --> 00:16:17,088
You didn't take the trophy.

327
00:16:20,220 --> 00:16:20,860
Wait.

328
00:16:21,300 --> 00:16:22,100
Stop.

329
00:16:23,260 --> 00:16:29,980
♪If back then we had never let go♪

330
00:16:30,740 --> 00:16:35,940
♪We wouldn't be lost in the crowd♪

331
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:40,140
♪We met in a thirteenth month♪

332
00:16:40,380 --> 00:16:41,980
♪Held each other in a fifth season♪

333
00:16:42,220 --> 00:16:43,860
♪And found our way back whole♪

334
00:16:43,860 --> 00:16:44,580
Doesn't it work?

335
00:16:44,820 --> 00:16:46,060
I am just not used to

336
00:16:46,060 --> 00:16:47,340
seeing you so proper.

337
00:16:48,580 --> 00:16:50,300
I am not used to your outfit either.

338
00:16:50,460 --> 00:16:51,540
Wearing pants under a skirt.

339
00:16:52,466 --> 00:16:53,420
What were you thinking?

340
00:16:53,420 --> 00:16:55,700
- Seriously? Is it not something new?
- Who did you learn that from?

341
00:16:55,700 --> 00:16:56,700
Just tell me if it looks good or not.

342
00:16:56,700 --> 00:16:58,340
Next time you get me a suit,

343
00:16:58,340 --> 00:17:00,020
can you make it a bit looser?

344
00:17:00,500 --> 00:17:02,500
These pants are way too tight today.

345
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:07,060
♪This one eternal photograph♪

346
00:17:07,940 --> 00:17:10,260
You wrote over
two million words in a year.

347
00:17:11,020 --> 00:17:12,940
Finally got a trophy like this,

348
00:17:12,940 --> 00:17:14,380
and I broke it.

349
00:17:15,020 --> 00:17:16,500
It's fine. It's just a trophy.

350
00:17:16,500 --> 00:17:17,560
If it's broken, it's fine.

351
00:17:17,570 --> 00:17:18,980
We got the honor, right?

352
00:17:19,220 --> 00:17:21,180
But the trophy matters, too.

353
00:17:22,220 --> 00:17:23,644
Then, we will write another one.

354
00:17:26,460 --> 00:17:28,220
Even if we do, it won't say

355
00:17:28,220 --> 00:17:31,420
Outstanding Author of 2021 anymore.

356
00:17:31,420 --> 00:17:32,410
Well, of course.

357
00:17:32,410 --> 00:17:33,700
Next year would be 2022, right?

358
00:18:30,380 --> 00:18:30,940
He Han, look.

359
00:18:32,220 --> 00:18:32,860
Found it.

360
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:34,220
Is that a preserved egg?

361
00:18:38,060 --> 00:18:38,380
Hey,

362
00:18:38,740 --> 00:18:39,540
don't fall asleep.

363
00:18:39,620 --> 00:18:40,380
I am not asleep.

364
00:18:41,940 --> 00:18:43,140
Stop lying.

365
00:18:43,980 --> 00:18:44,540
Wake up.

366
00:18:46,620 --> 00:18:47,940
I heard it.

367
00:18:48,620 --> 00:18:49,780
I was not snoring.

368
00:18:50,740 --> 00:18:52,180
Then, who was snoring?

369
00:18:59,180 --> 00:19:02,500
(He Han, The Desert Rises to Fame)

370
00:19:16,420 --> 00:19:20,900
(He Han, The Desert Rises to Fame)

371
00:20:05,866 --> 00:20:06,970
You are not sleepy, right?

372
00:20:07,220 --> 00:20:07,780
No.

373
00:20:08,111 --> 00:20:08,977
You are sleepy?

374
00:20:09,420 --> 00:20:09,900
I am not.

375
00:20:10,088 --> 00:20:11,822
How could I feel
sleepy when I am with you?

376
00:20:12,066 --> 00:20:13,666
I am not disturbing your work, am I?

377
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:14,444
Not at all.

378
00:20:15,340 --> 00:20:15,900
That is good.

379
00:20:37,020 --> 00:20:38,260
You came back late tonight.

380
00:20:38,666 --> 00:20:40,260
We even went to the police station.

381
00:20:40,660 --> 00:20:42,111
Zhang Yousen got into a fight.

382
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:43,260
What about now?

383
00:20:43,700 --> 00:20:44,420
Is he all right?

384
00:20:45,260 --> 00:20:45,900
He is fine.

385
00:20:47,660 --> 00:20:48,820
Why did he get into a fight?

386
00:20:49,980 --> 00:20:51,540
Just a young man trying to show off.

387
00:20:51,600 --> 00:20:52,977
Picking trouble for no reason.

388
00:21:01,060 --> 00:21:01,660
Nice.

389
00:21:11,222 --> 00:21:12,444
What are you doing?

390
00:21:12,900 --> 00:21:14,140
Showing respect to a beauty.

391
00:21:19,688 --> 00:21:21,066
Zhou Mei, you should go first.

392
00:21:34,933 --> 00:21:36,777
Do you know
how awkward this is for me?

393
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,260
I am already in my thirties,

394
00:21:38,260 --> 00:21:39,866
yet I still have to watch my boyfriend

395
00:21:39,888 --> 00:21:41,577
rolling around
on the ground with a thug.

396
00:21:42,980 --> 00:21:43,940
It's always like that.

397
00:21:44,620 --> 00:21:45,866
You cannot just avoid it.

398
00:21:46,260 --> 00:21:47,700
What about your other boyfriends?

399
00:21:47,710 --> 00:21:49,466
What would they do
in a situation like this?

400
00:21:49,500 --> 00:21:50,955
Why are you not going to sleep?

401
00:21:51,140 --> 00:21:52,300
With a topic this interesting,

402
00:21:52,300 --> 00:21:53,488
I would be wide awake.

403
00:21:55,140 --> 00:21:56,260
My other boyfriends

404
00:21:56,466 --> 00:21:58,155
wouldn't do something like this.

405
00:21:59,220 --> 00:22:00,580
Look at you,

406
00:22:00,688 --> 00:22:02,222
spending all night with Zhang Yousen

407
00:22:02,260 --> 00:22:04,022
playing games until
dawn before coming back.

408
00:22:04,100 --> 00:22:05,200
What are you trying to do?

409
00:22:05,244 --> 00:22:06,733
Well, when you are in a relationship,

410
00:22:06,780 --> 00:22:08,977
you have to do something
to pass the long nights.

411
00:22:09,260 --> 00:22:10,580
If you go home right after dinner,

412
00:22:10,740 --> 00:22:11,940
it kills the mood.

413
00:22:13,060 --> 00:22:14,700
Going to a hotel or watching a movie...

414
00:22:15,220 --> 00:22:17,060
I am not in the mood
for that with him yet.

415
00:22:22,980 --> 00:22:23,540
Go to sleep.

416
00:22:28,140 --> 00:22:28,940
Go to sleep.

417
00:22:47,488 --> 00:22:49,980
(Zhanqiao: You are waiting
for Lawyer Bei to come find you.)

418
00:23:10,460 --> 00:23:16,300
(May: He owes me an explanation.)

419
00:23:39,900 --> 00:23:40,755
Hello, what is it?

420
00:23:41,140 --> 00:23:41,977
Are you at home?

421
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:44,290
I want you to help buy
breakfast for my grandmother.

422
00:23:44,300 --> 00:23:45,977
She cannot take her medicine
on an empty stomach.

423
00:23:46,066 --> 00:23:47,100
The helper stopped coming.

424
00:23:47,311 --> 00:23:48,177
I am on my way now.

425
00:23:52,020 --> 00:23:52,420
Thank you.

426
00:23:52,540 --> 00:23:52,940
Take care.

427
00:24:18,460 --> 00:24:19,260
Min.

428
00:24:19,780 --> 00:24:20,250
Grandma.

429
00:24:20,250 --> 00:24:22,060
I am Ling Yikai's girlfriend.

430
00:24:22,140 --> 00:24:23,060
My name is Zhao Lanxin.

431
00:24:23,340 --> 00:24:24,380
I brought you breakfast.

432
00:24:24,488 --> 00:24:25,650
You haven't eaten yet, right?

433
00:24:25,660 --> 00:24:26,460
Where is Min?

434
00:24:27,311 --> 00:24:29,100
She has something to
take care of these days.

435
00:24:29,180 --> 00:24:30,540
Ling Yikai asked me to come.

436
00:24:32,780 --> 00:24:34,580
I brought you vegetable buns,

437
00:24:35,180 --> 00:24:35,780
Shaomai,

438
00:24:35,860 --> 00:24:36,700
wonton,

439
00:24:37,020 --> 00:24:37,780
and soy milk.

440
00:24:38,220 --> 00:24:38,700
Come, sit.

441
00:24:39,460 --> 00:24:40,460
Which one would you like?

442
00:24:41,460 --> 00:24:42,300
I won't eat.

443
00:24:43,060 --> 00:24:44,020
I'll wait for Min.

444
00:24:45,340 --> 00:24:45,780
Grandma,

445
00:24:46,220 --> 00:24:46,900
it's like this.

446
00:24:47,620 --> 00:24:49,340
I am staying next door now.

447
00:24:49,533 --> 00:24:51,466
The helper has
something to handle these days,

448
00:24:51,511 --> 00:24:52,955
so I am bringing your meals.

449
00:24:53,260 --> 00:24:55,860
You have to take
these medicines after eating.

450
00:24:56,260 --> 00:24:57,100
If you don't eat now,

451
00:24:57,100 --> 00:24:58,911
it will be past the time to take them.

452
00:24:59,140 --> 00:24:59,620
But...

453
00:25:00,380 --> 00:25:02,540
I don't even know
what medicine I am taking.

454
00:25:03,100 --> 00:25:04,260
Min always

455
00:25:04,260 --> 00:25:05,860
prepared them for me.

456
00:25:07,060 --> 00:25:07,700
Grandma,

457
00:25:08,060 --> 00:25:08,900
it's all right.

458
00:25:08,980 --> 00:25:10,820
I have checked and memorized everything.

459
00:25:11,540 --> 00:25:12,860
Losartan potassium tablets,

460
00:25:13,220 --> 00:25:14,660
metformin capsules,

461
00:25:14,980 --> 00:25:16,140
and triamterene tablets.

462
00:25:16,511 --> 00:25:17,577
Did I get them right?

463
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:20,340
I am so sorry.

464
00:25:20,780 --> 00:25:21,740
Min didn't

465
00:25:21,820 --> 00:25:22,660
inform us.

466
00:25:22,660 --> 00:25:23,888
She just left on her own.

467
00:25:25,860 --> 00:25:27,380
Actually, Mr. Ling, you know...

468
00:25:28,220 --> 00:25:29,540
It's not easy to find a helper

469
00:25:29,940 --> 00:25:31,020
for your grandmother.

470
00:25:31,860 --> 00:25:33,340
Min left because

471
00:25:33,555 --> 00:25:34,820
it's too dark here at night.

472
00:25:34,900 --> 00:25:36,100
She could not settle in here,

473
00:25:36,500 --> 00:25:37,060
so she left.

474
00:25:38,180 --> 00:25:38,900
I understand.

475
00:25:41,980 --> 00:25:42,820
I'll pay more.

476
00:25:43,844 --> 00:25:45,280
Please help me find someone suitable.

477
00:25:45,290 --> 00:25:45,955
Help me.

478
00:25:46,460 --> 00:25:46,860
Please.

479
00:25:49,500 --> 00:25:49,980
Grandma,

480
00:25:50,260 --> 00:25:52,300
let me show you how
to recognize these pills.

481
00:25:52,377 --> 00:25:54,140
Just in case you need
to take them yourself,

482
00:25:54,260 --> 00:25:55,660
or someone else gives them to you,

483
00:25:55,670 --> 00:25:56,540
you will at least know

484
00:25:56,540 --> 00:25:57,540
what you are taking.

485
00:25:58,220 --> 00:25:58,620
Alright.

486
00:25:59,140 --> 00:25:59,460
Come.

487
00:26:00,180 --> 00:26:01,533
Grandma, give me your hand.

488
00:26:04,140 --> 00:26:05,820
Let's feel this capsule first.

489
00:26:06,980 --> 00:26:09,100
This is the metformin capsule.

490
00:26:09,900 --> 00:26:10,740
Can you feel

491
00:26:10,860 --> 00:26:11,980
the shape of the capsule?

492
00:26:12,820 --> 00:26:13,210
Alright.

493
00:26:13,210 --> 00:26:14,420
Let's try another one.

494
00:26:14,540 --> 00:26:15,060
This one.

495
00:26:15,260 --> 00:26:16,340
Oval-shaped,

496
00:26:16,580 --> 00:26:17,980
a little thicker.

497
00:26:18,940 --> 00:26:20,660
This is the losartan potassium tablet.

498
00:26:24,020 --> 00:26:24,700
Can you feel it?

499
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:26,850
There is another one that is similar.

500
00:26:26,860 --> 00:26:27,940
Here, give me your hand.

501
00:26:28,500 --> 00:26:29,980
This one is also oval-shaped.

502
00:26:41,100 --> 00:26:43,180
Before the agency finds a new helper,

503
00:26:43,180 --> 00:26:44,260
you can leave Grandma to me.

504
00:26:49,066 --> 00:26:51,377
It will still take another week.
Aren't you going to work?

505
00:26:51,900 --> 00:26:52,860
It's just one week.

506
00:26:53,060 --> 00:26:54,311
I can take her with me to work.

507
00:27:03,220 --> 00:27:03,660
Thank you.

508
00:27:06,644 --> 00:27:07,511
I am leaving.

509
00:27:28,540 --> 00:27:30,380
When you go to
the office later, and they ask,

510
00:27:30,460 --> 00:27:32,022
think about what you are going to say.

511
00:27:32,340 --> 00:27:32,780
It's fine.

512
00:27:33,260 --> 00:27:34,488
Lawyer Bei already knows.

513
00:27:36,340 --> 00:27:37,340
No idea who

514
00:27:37,460 --> 00:27:38,780
was so quick to pass it on.

515
00:27:42,300 --> 00:27:43,980
So, what did he say to you?

516
00:27:44,660 --> 00:27:45,940
He asked about what happened.

517
00:27:47,020 --> 00:27:48,420
I figured there was nothing

518
00:27:48,900 --> 00:27:49,820
I couldn't tell him,

519
00:27:50,380 --> 00:27:51,300
so I told him.

520
00:27:51,600 --> 00:27:52,577
Who would have thought

521
00:27:53,260 --> 00:27:54,820
that he thinks being in a relationship

522
00:27:54,820 --> 00:27:56,066
is affecting my work.

523
00:27:56,222 --> 00:27:57,800
He told me to weigh the pros and cons

524
00:27:57,940 --> 00:27:58,940
and promise him

525
00:27:59,340 --> 00:28:01,020
that work comes before love.

526
00:28:01,380 --> 00:28:02,059
Otherwise,

527
00:28:02,060 --> 00:28:03,620
he will reconsider whether I stay.

528
00:28:05,220 --> 00:28:06,380
As your supervisor,

529
00:28:06,466 --> 00:28:09,111
it's fair that he said something after
you ended up at the police station.

530
00:28:09,180 --> 00:28:11,022
He has never really
been in a relationship.

531
00:28:11,820 --> 00:28:12,380
Or rather,

532
00:28:12,780 --> 00:28:14,180
he has never truly loved someone.

533
00:28:14,180 --> 00:28:15,377
So he wouldn't understand.

534
00:28:15,660 --> 00:28:16,900
When he married his wife,

535
00:28:17,180 --> 00:28:18,860
it was because of her family background.

536
00:28:19,500 --> 00:28:20,220
I told him

537
00:28:20,980 --> 00:28:22,580
the fight was my responsibility.

538
00:28:22,700 --> 00:28:23,620
It won't happen again.

539
00:28:23,911 --> 00:28:26,666
But asking me to restrain my
relationship? It's not going to happen.

540
00:28:26,860 --> 00:28:28,700
People may be able to stop many things,

541
00:28:29,020 --> 00:28:30,900
but the one thing
they cannot stop is love.

542
00:28:30,900 --> 00:28:31,260
Right?

543
00:28:31,340 --> 00:28:31,860
Then,

544
00:28:33,140 --> 00:28:33,980
what did he say?

545
00:28:34,580 --> 00:28:35,420
He asked me

546
00:28:35,540 --> 00:28:36,860
to pause my work

547
00:28:37,300 --> 00:28:38,860
and take two days to write a reflection.

548
00:28:39,580 --> 00:28:40,300
What is that?

549
00:28:40,577 --> 00:28:41,666
Am I a school student?

550
00:28:42,340 --> 00:28:43,260
Not allowed to date?

551
00:28:43,688 --> 00:28:44,940
He can fire me if he wants,

552
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,533
but I am not writing any reflection.

553
00:28:46,740 --> 00:28:47,780
If he really fires me,

554
00:28:48,060 --> 00:28:49,340
I'll tell everyone at the firm

555
00:28:49,460 --> 00:28:50,260
that I was dismissed

556
00:28:50,260 --> 00:28:51,511
because I believe in love.

557
00:28:54,060 --> 00:28:54,820
Pull over.

558
00:28:57,222 --> 00:28:58,022
Alright.

559
00:29:02,333 --> 00:29:03,940
I'll take a taxi back to the office.

560
00:29:04,022 --> 00:29:05,533
You go back and write the reflection.

561
00:29:05,644 --> 00:29:07,844
Submit it to Lawyer Bei
before the end of the day.

562
00:29:08,060 --> 00:29:09,740
If you lose this job,

563
00:29:09,740 --> 00:29:10,688
then we are done.

564
00:29:10,755 --> 00:29:12,155
Do not feel pressured.

565
00:29:12,177 --> 00:29:13,780
What I choose to do is my own decision.

566
00:29:13,780 --> 00:29:15,150
It has nothing to do with you, Zhou Mei.

567
00:29:15,177 --> 00:29:16,066
I am not joking.

568
00:29:31,780 --> 00:29:33,060
Are you free at noon?

569
00:29:33,377 --> 00:29:34,400
I want to see you.

570
00:29:47,140 --> 00:29:48,380
I was about to find you

571
00:29:48,740 --> 00:29:50,060
if you hadn't come to me.

572
00:29:51,777 --> 00:29:53,422
You are not planning
to fire Zhang Yousen

573
00:29:53,430 --> 00:29:54,333
over this, are you?

574
00:29:54,540 --> 00:29:56,220
If he gets dismissed now, it'll be hard

575
00:29:56,644 --> 00:29:58,266
for him to find another job later.

576
00:29:58,780 --> 00:30:00,540
I am not going to fire Zhang Yousen.

577
00:30:01,380 --> 00:30:04,300
But for his inappropriate behavior,

578
00:30:05,100 --> 00:30:06,980
asking him to write a reflection

579
00:30:07,644 --> 00:30:09,444
is part of company policy, right?

580
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:11,860
What if he refuses?

581
00:30:16,220 --> 00:30:17,460
Then, I'll write it for him.

582
00:30:20,540 --> 00:30:22,020
He is young and capable,

583
00:30:22,620 --> 00:30:24,580
and he hasn't done
anything unforgivable.

584
00:30:24,580 --> 00:30:26,180
Why would I fire him?

585
00:30:26,780 --> 00:30:27,500
But...

586
00:30:28,620 --> 00:30:29,220
But what?

587
00:30:31,820 --> 00:30:32,780
I hope you

588
00:30:33,700 --> 00:30:34,940
don't hold back his future.

589
00:30:36,540 --> 00:30:37,860
I am holding back his future?

590
00:30:37,911 --> 00:30:38,780
Do you know that now

591
00:30:38,780 --> 00:30:40,660
he goes to work every day,
looking worn out?

592
00:30:41,488 --> 00:30:43,288
With dark circles under his eyes,

593
00:30:43,900 --> 00:30:45,260
he even dozes off during meetings.

594
00:30:45,780 --> 00:30:47,820
It's already affecting the company.

595
00:30:47,940 --> 00:30:48,900
And all of this

596
00:30:50,180 --> 00:30:51,340
is because of you.

597
00:30:57,420 --> 00:30:58,180
I plan

598
00:30:58,900 --> 00:30:59,620
to transfer him

599
00:30:59,733 --> 00:31:01,133
to the Southwest Branch.

600
00:31:04,066 --> 00:31:05,540
What if he does not want to go?

601
00:31:05,733 --> 00:31:07,020
After two years, he can come back

602
00:31:07,540 --> 00:31:08,780
and apply for his license.

603
00:31:09,420 --> 00:31:11,420
Then, he can take cases on his own

604
00:31:12,100 --> 00:31:13,500
and build up his own clients.

605
00:31:13,860 --> 00:31:14,940
In a few years,

606
00:31:15,066 --> 00:31:17,422
he might even become
the youngest partner in the firm.

607
00:31:17,580 --> 00:31:18,540
If it were me,

608
00:31:18,733 --> 00:31:20,311
I would want that opportunity.

609
00:31:21,220 --> 00:31:22,620
You are trying to send him away

610
00:31:22,777 --> 00:31:24,400
because you are jealous, right?

611
00:31:28,260 --> 00:31:30,380
I don't want you making use
of an innocent young man.

612
00:31:32,140 --> 00:31:34,420
I have every reason to dismiss him,

613
00:31:34,860 --> 00:31:35,780
but I believe

614
00:31:35,933 --> 00:31:37,844
you wouldn't want to see that happen.

615
00:31:39,340 --> 00:31:40,660
Many relationships begin

616
00:31:41,100 --> 00:31:42,020
by accident,

617
00:31:42,311 --> 00:31:43,711
in a moment of impulse.

618
00:31:44,980 --> 00:31:46,500
If you have any issues with me,

619
00:31:46,500 --> 00:31:47,420
take it out on me.

620
00:31:47,666 --> 00:31:49,377
Do not drag innocent people into it.

621
00:31:49,500 --> 00:31:51,420
That will only bring you more trouble.

622
00:31:58,177 --> 00:32:00,060
What right do I have
to take issue with you?

623
00:32:08,020 --> 00:32:10,180
Shouldn't everything
between us be pleasant?

624
00:32:10,940 --> 00:32:13,260
We are the best gift
life has given each other.

625
00:32:14,660 --> 00:32:16,220
Even if life is a mess,

626
00:32:16,860 --> 00:32:17,980
having this gift

627
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:19,890
is still something to be glad about.

628
00:32:19,890 --> 00:32:21,955
Then, don't let me
run into your wife again.

629
00:32:23,220 --> 00:32:24,420
I know you are married.

630
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:27,288
I also know that it's your boundary.

631
00:32:28,060 --> 00:32:29,860
So you don't need to say it to my face.

632
00:32:30,940 --> 00:32:31,660
Doing that

633
00:32:32,580 --> 00:32:34,260
only makes me feel you look down on me

634
00:32:34,820 --> 00:32:36,220
or on what we have.

635
00:32:43,020 --> 00:32:44,900
When I have gatherings with friends,

636
00:32:45,020 --> 00:32:45,980
if my wife is free,

637
00:32:45,980 --> 00:32:47,220
I bring her along.

638
00:32:48,500 --> 00:32:49,330
Usually,

639
00:32:49,330 --> 00:32:51,380
I don't get many chances
to have meals with her.

640
00:32:52,700 --> 00:32:54,780
I am not always willing,

641
00:32:55,460 --> 00:32:56,140
but...

642
00:32:58,140 --> 00:32:59,460
sometimes, I feel

643
00:33:00,660 --> 00:33:01,940
I should.

644
00:33:05,540 --> 00:33:06,780
Let me tell you one more thing.

645
00:33:09,260 --> 00:33:10,860
Your wife has probably noticed us.

646
00:33:13,688 --> 00:33:15,500
Do not underestimate
a woman's intuition.

647
00:33:16,900 --> 00:33:17,540
This time,

648
00:33:18,660 --> 00:33:19,820
you made it worse.

649
00:33:21,860 --> 00:33:22,700
So, I suggest

650
00:33:23,300 --> 00:33:24,660
you don't send Zhang Yousen away.

651
00:33:25,700 --> 00:33:26,940
Otherwise, your wife will think

652
00:33:27,333 --> 00:33:28,933
it's because you are jealous.

653
00:33:32,220 --> 00:33:33,900
I'll handle things with Zhang Yousen.

654
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:35,977
He shouldn't be dragged into this.

655
00:33:36,511 --> 00:33:38,420
Since we both think he
is a good young man,

656
00:33:39,140 --> 00:33:39,900
let's

657
00:33:40,460 --> 00:33:41,100
protect him.

658
00:33:51,620 --> 00:33:52,300
Mrs. Bei,

659
00:33:53,133 --> 00:33:54,444
what a coincidence.

660
00:33:58,200 --> 00:33:59,622
I came to see him about something.

661
00:33:59,630 --> 00:34:01,866
The secretary said
he was dining here, so I came over.

662
00:34:02,580 --> 00:34:04,860
I am here to speak to Lawyer Bei
on Zhang Yousen's behalf.

663
00:34:05,220 --> 00:34:06,180
He made a small mistake.

664
00:34:06,266 --> 00:34:07,460
Please give him another chance.

665
00:34:07,577 --> 00:34:08,488
It won't happen again.

666
00:34:11,044 --> 00:34:12,160
Another place setting, please.

667
00:34:12,177 --> 00:34:13,488
Ma'am, your utensils.

668
00:34:22,733 --> 00:34:23,420
Please enjoy.

669
00:34:23,555 --> 00:34:23,940
Thank you.

670
00:34:24,020 --> 00:34:24,666
Thank you.

671
00:34:25,620 --> 00:34:26,500
I didn't expect

672
00:34:27,060 --> 00:34:28,660
you to care so much

673
00:34:28,733 --> 00:34:30,200
about your boyfriend, Miss Zhou.

674
00:34:30,380 --> 00:34:31,980
I thought someone like you

675
00:34:32,260 --> 00:34:32,940
would have men

676
00:34:33,060 --> 00:34:34,940
caring about you instead.

677
00:34:37,300 --> 00:34:39,060
Whether someone cares is fate.

678
00:34:39,260 --> 00:34:40,780
It has nothing to do with looks.

679
00:34:42,100 --> 00:34:43,140
I have never had

680
00:34:43,780 --> 00:34:45,140
an easy life.

681
00:34:46,780 --> 00:34:48,420
Zhang Yousen is a good young man.

682
00:34:49,140 --> 00:34:51,820
But forgive me for saying this,

683
00:34:52,540 --> 00:34:53,100
Miss Zhou,

684
00:34:53,222 --> 00:34:54,266
with your conditions,

685
00:34:54,500 --> 00:34:55,540
you should find someone

686
00:34:56,380 --> 00:34:58,340
better, someone who can take care of you

687
00:34:58,500 --> 00:34:59,060
and let you

688
00:34:59,340 --> 00:35:00,460
live without worry.

689
00:35:00,540 --> 00:35:00,940
Right?

690
00:35:04,300 --> 00:35:05,111
Alright then.

691
00:35:05,580 --> 00:35:06,860
If there is a chance,

692
00:35:07,133 --> 00:35:08,777
Mrs. Bei, please
introduce someone to me.

693
00:35:12,180 --> 00:35:13,380
I'll find time

694
00:35:13,620 --> 00:35:15,220
to speak to Zhang Yousen.

695
00:35:16,260 --> 00:35:17,180
I hope you

696
00:35:17,260 --> 00:35:19,200
will also remind him
to focus on his work

697
00:35:19,540 --> 00:35:20,620
and not let play

698
00:35:20,980 --> 00:35:22,300
delay what matters.

699
00:35:22,660 --> 00:35:23,060
Alright.

700
00:35:23,540 --> 00:35:24,644
Thank you, Lawyer Bei.

701
00:35:25,900 --> 00:35:27,370
Please enjoy your meal.

702
00:35:27,370 --> 00:35:28,377
I'll take my leave.

703
00:35:28,780 --> 00:35:29,688
Excuse me, the bill.

704
00:35:30,140 --> 00:35:31,300
No need. I'll pay.

705
00:35:31,580 --> 00:35:32,100
You go ahead.

706
00:35:32,620 --> 00:35:34,500
I asked for your help,
so I cannot let you pay.

707
00:35:35,180 --> 00:35:35,700
It's fine.

708
00:36:13,420 --> 00:36:15,340
At last night's Author Night,

709
00:36:15,660 --> 00:36:16,580
the spotlight

710
00:36:17,100 --> 00:36:17,860
belonged to Gu Yan.

711
00:36:19,260 --> 00:36:20,220
But Lin Zhanqiao

712
00:36:21,060 --> 00:36:21,820
belonged to He Han.

713
00:36:23,980 --> 00:36:25,540
At a time like this, we,

714
00:36:25,740 --> 00:36:27,540
especially you, should give it a push.

715
00:36:27,688 --> 00:36:29,177
What is broken can come back together.

716
00:36:31,060 --> 00:36:32,580
May I ask you something?

717
00:36:32,740 --> 00:36:34,155
Ask as many as you like.

718
00:36:35,700 --> 00:36:39,260
Earlier, when Zhiyuan withdrew
their investment from Lin Zhanqiao,

719
00:36:40,140 --> 00:36:42,340
was it you or Zhao Lanxin

720
00:36:42,340 --> 00:36:43,460
who tipped them off?

721
00:36:44,860 --> 00:36:45,580
Look,

722
00:36:46,660 --> 00:36:48,180
Zhiyuan already

723
00:36:48,260 --> 00:36:49,500
made it clear.

724
00:36:49,860 --> 00:36:50,180
Right?

725
00:36:50,580 --> 00:36:52,220
It was just a coincidence.

726
00:36:54,180 --> 00:36:57,420
They were eating there,
and someone at the next table

727
00:36:57,420 --> 00:36:59,000
was talking about Lin Zhanqiao's

728
00:36:59,088 --> 00:37:01,540
newly signed authors,
saying she could not pay them.

729
00:37:01,620 --> 00:37:03,540
And it just so happened
you were at that table.

730
00:37:05,140 --> 00:37:05,740
Well...

731
00:37:06,580 --> 00:37:08,380
How would I know someone was listening?

732
00:37:08,380 --> 00:37:11,260
So, all of this was your doing.

733
00:37:11,700 --> 00:37:14,130
On one hand,

734
00:37:14,130 --> 00:37:16,288
you shook the investor's
confidence in Lin Zhanqiao,

735
00:37:16,540 --> 00:37:18,820
and on the other,
you had Zhao Lanxin intercept

736
00:37:18,820 --> 00:37:20,820
new authors
Lin Zhanqiao hadn't paid yet.

737
00:37:21,820 --> 00:37:22,780
And on your side,

738
00:37:23,260 --> 00:37:25,540
you pretend to be so loyal

739
00:37:26,180 --> 00:37:27,420
and ready to take over anytime.

740
00:37:28,600 --> 00:37:30,044
I did all this because of you.

741
00:37:33,660 --> 00:37:34,300
Because I know

742
00:37:35,580 --> 00:37:37,940
you are worried
they might get back together,

743
00:37:38,620 --> 00:37:39,020
right?

744
00:37:44,380 --> 00:37:47,100
After all, you are new here.

745
00:37:49,177 --> 00:37:50,533
If you don't want to eat, get out.

746
00:37:50,940 --> 00:37:51,580
I eat.

747
00:37:53,780 --> 00:37:54,100
I eat.

748
00:37:56,180 --> 00:37:58,288
(Dingqi Author Night ends,
lighting up Shanghai.)

749
00:38:03,540 --> 00:38:04,180
Mantou,

750
00:38:04,740 --> 00:38:05,580
is this true?

751
00:38:06,180 --> 00:38:07,700
So, Mr. He Han is coming back?

752
00:38:08,260 --> 00:38:09,500
Most likely.

753
00:38:09,977 --> 00:38:10,940
When Ms. Lin comes later,

754
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:12,420
don't start gossiping.

755
00:38:12,500 --> 00:38:13,700
Let her announce it herself.

756
00:38:13,940 --> 00:38:15,580
After all that, they are back together.

757
00:38:15,580 --> 00:38:17,422
Looks like wedding candy
is coming this time.

758
00:38:17,430 --> 00:38:18,330
They should have
gotten married long ago.

759
00:38:18,340 --> 00:38:19,170
It's not too late.

760
00:38:19,170 --> 00:38:21,177
Had they married early,
they might have divorced early too.

761
00:38:21,180 --> 00:38:22,340
But recently, I thought

762
00:38:22,340 --> 00:38:23,780
our boss and Gu Yan were together.

763
00:38:23,780 --> 00:38:26,130
Once you have seen the ocean,
no other water compares, you know?

764
00:38:26,140 --> 00:38:27,860
Gu Yan left with our boss yesterday.

765
00:38:27,911 --> 00:38:29,155
Why are there no photos of them?

766
00:38:29,340 --> 00:38:29,980
Who knows?

767
00:38:30,300 --> 00:38:31,020
Zhangzhu,

768
00:38:31,380 --> 00:38:32,900
you are with our boss every day.

769
00:38:32,900 --> 00:38:34,180
Any inside news?

770
00:38:34,700 --> 00:38:35,700
I didn't notice anything.

771
00:38:35,980 --> 00:38:36,420
Ms. Lin.

772
00:38:37,900 --> 00:38:38,300
Ms. Lin.

773
00:38:38,500 --> 00:38:39,980
These are the updated drafts.

774
00:38:44,466 --> 00:38:45,660
Has Gu Yan submitted his draft?

775
00:38:46,060 --> 00:38:47,420
Not yet. I'll remind him now.

776
00:38:47,866 --> 00:38:48,900
I'll go to him myself.

777
00:38:49,780 --> 00:38:50,260
Okay.

778
00:39:08,420 --> 00:39:09,500
The update is not ready yet?

779
00:39:10,300 --> 00:39:11,133
I am writing it.

780
00:39:11,660 --> 00:39:12,800
I'll send it to you later.

781
00:39:13,300 --> 00:39:14,666
You don't need to come here.

782
00:39:15,700 --> 00:39:16,740
Then, we will talk later.

783
00:39:16,955 --> 00:39:18,460
I have a project meeting this afternoon.

784
00:39:18,460 --> 00:39:19,820
After it ends, I'll come to you.

785
00:39:23,220 --> 00:39:26,180
Lin Zhanqiao, He Han,
and I used to be colleagues.

786
00:39:27,020 --> 00:39:28,460
So I saw their relationship

787
00:39:28,460 --> 00:39:29,620
with my own eyes.

788
00:39:30,820 --> 00:39:32,650
You wouldn't want He Han to come back

789
00:39:32,650 --> 00:39:34,020
and work with Lin Zhanqiao again.

790
00:39:34,980 --> 00:39:36,260
Emotionally,

791
00:39:36,355 --> 00:39:38,660
they are old lovers,
reuniting after a long separation.

792
00:39:39,066 --> 00:39:41,622
Their closeness will
definitely be stronger than before.

793
00:39:42,140 --> 00:39:42,860
And accordingly,

794
00:39:42,860 --> 00:39:44,060
the time she spends on you

795
00:39:44,300 --> 00:39:45,340
will decrease.

796
00:39:46,540 --> 00:39:46,900
Second,

797
00:39:47,340 --> 00:39:48,500
for Dingqi,

798
00:39:48,900 --> 00:39:49,940
publicity aside,

799
00:39:50,100 --> 00:39:51,660
He Han is still more valuable than you.

800
00:39:52,377 --> 00:39:54,755
Once you start competing
under the same company,

801
00:39:55,060 --> 00:39:56,180
wherever you go,

802
00:39:56,580 --> 00:39:58,220
you will still be
overshadowed by He Han.

803
00:39:58,644 --> 00:39:59,822
You want to poach me?

804
00:40:00,100 --> 00:40:01,300
Of course, you would say that.

805
00:40:01,380 --> 00:40:03,200
I don't deny that I want to poach you.

806
00:40:03,500 --> 00:40:04,860
Otherwise, why would I come to you?

807
00:40:06,860 --> 00:40:08,420
But I am not trying to force you.

808
00:40:09,100 --> 00:40:10,930
Nor do I expect that after hearing this,

809
00:40:10,930 --> 00:40:12,180
you will lean toward me.

810
00:40:13,300 --> 00:40:14,020
I have always

811
00:40:14,260 --> 00:40:15,820
done better than I speak.

812
00:40:17,460 --> 00:40:18,780
As long as you give me a chance,

813
00:40:19,100 --> 00:40:20,020
I'll show you

814
00:40:20,420 --> 00:40:22,180
what it means to value you

815
00:40:22,288 --> 00:40:25,155
and what it means to see you as the
most important person in the company.

816
00:40:25,180 --> 00:40:26,311
From nothing to something,

817
00:40:26,511 --> 00:40:28,888
it was Lin Zhanqiao who
helped me find my worth.

818
00:40:29,460 --> 00:40:30,340
At least for now,

819
00:40:30,340 --> 00:40:32,133
I am still her most important author.

820
00:40:36,060 --> 00:40:36,980
To be fair,

821
00:40:37,460 --> 00:40:39,420
Lin Zhanqiao never really spent

822
00:40:39,420 --> 00:40:40,577
that much time on you.

823
00:40:41,540 --> 00:40:42,660
You have had it hard.

824
00:40:42,900 --> 00:40:45,333
You are used to no one
managing you or caring about you.

825
00:40:45,511 --> 00:40:47,660
So, when Lin Zhanqiao
gives you a little sweetness,

826
00:40:47,688 --> 00:40:49,488
you think you have
gained the whole world.

827
00:40:50,460 --> 00:40:51,380
Without comparison,

828
00:40:51,740 --> 00:40:52,820
don't rush to conclusions.

829
00:40:52,820 --> 00:40:54,600
I think things are already good now.

830
00:40:54,780 --> 00:40:56,780
I trust Lin Zhanqiao.
I don't need comparisons.

831
00:40:59,780 --> 00:41:01,460
I just don't want He Han's arrival

832
00:41:02,140 --> 00:41:03,620
to change how things are now.

833
00:41:06,540 --> 00:41:07,700
I am only telling you

834
00:41:08,100 --> 00:41:09,180
that you deserve better.

835
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:12,540
I'll go now.

836
00:41:12,955 --> 00:41:14,460
Otherwise, if Lin Zhanqiao comes

837
00:41:14,460 --> 00:41:15,540
and sees me here with you,

838
00:41:15,580 --> 00:41:17,350
you'll have an even
harder time explaining it.

839
00:41:21,860 --> 00:41:22,820
Call me anytime.

840
00:41:23,100 --> 00:41:24,100
Twenty-four hours a day.

841
00:41:24,340 --> 00:41:25,980
Call me when you have no one to talk to.

842
00:41:36,460 --> 00:41:37,740
Xiaolongbao. Enjoy.

843
00:41:37,980 --> 00:41:38,540
Thank you.

844
00:41:59,900 --> 00:42:00,300
Hello?

845
00:42:00,688 --> 00:42:01,822
What are you doing?

846
00:42:01,933 --> 00:42:03,777
Has Mr. Fan's contract been signed?

847
00:42:03,780 --> 00:42:05,466
I have already
revised it and sent it over,

848
00:42:05,470 --> 00:42:06,844
but he hasn't replied yet.

849
00:42:06,940 --> 00:42:07,822
Did you chase him?

850
00:42:08,020 --> 00:42:08,420
No.

851
00:42:09,500 --> 00:42:10,260
That is right.

852
00:42:10,540 --> 00:42:12,780
The more casual you seem now,
the better. Understand?

853
00:42:13,500 --> 00:42:15,300
And you can even make the contract terms

854
00:42:15,300 --> 00:42:16,500
a little tougher.

855
00:42:16,500 --> 00:42:17,740
The harder you are to deal with,

856
00:42:17,740 --> 00:42:19,977
the more determined
he will be to get it. Understand?

857
00:42:20,700 --> 00:42:21,777
What are you doing tonight?

858
00:42:21,980 --> 00:42:23,100
How about we go watch a movie

859
00:42:23,300 --> 00:42:24,466
and give it a push?

860
00:42:27,700 --> 00:42:28,940
Or we can just have dinner.

861
00:42:29,220 --> 00:42:30,444
I happen to discuss with you.

862
00:42:31,155 --> 00:42:33,088
Tonight, at the French restaurant
near Chenxing.

863
00:42:33,100 --> 00:42:34,177
I'll book the table.

864
00:42:34,644 --> 00:42:36,600
When the time comes, we split the bill.

865
00:42:38,266 --> 00:42:40,180
Dinner is fine,
but no splitting the bill.

866
00:42:40,300 --> 00:42:41,650
I am here to help you.

867
00:42:41,650 --> 00:42:43,380
You should pay for the meal, right?

868
00:42:46,700 --> 00:42:47,140
Fine.

869
00:42:48,044 --> 00:42:49,000
See you tonight.

870
00:43:05,921 --> 00:43:07,041
(I've been thinking.)

871
00:43:08,321 --> 00:43:11,601
(Everyone's most comfortable level of intimacy)

872
00:43:12,361 --> 00:43:19,691
(is probably different.)

873
00:43:20,691 --> 00:43:22,441
♪If the sky♪

874
00:43:22,951 --> 00:43:24,351
♪And the sea♪

875
00:43:24,891 --> 00:43:26,601
♪Turned upside down♪

876
00:43:28,161 --> 00:43:30,091
♪If a swimming fish♪

877
00:43:30,491 --> 00:43:33,881
♪Fell in love with a flying bird♪

878
00:43:35,651 --> 00:43:37,621
♪If back then♪

879
00:43:37,981 --> 00:43:42,391
♪We had never let go♪

880
00:43:42,991 --> 00:43:49,271
♪We wouldn't be lost in the crowd♪

881
00:43:50,391 --> 00:43:52,541
♪We met in a thirteenth month♪

882
00:43:52,541 --> 00:43:54,411
♪Held each other in a fifth season♪

883
00:43:54,591 --> 00:43:57,031
♪And found our way back whole♪

884
00:43:57,871 --> 00:44:00,041
♪So let this surging love♪

885
00:44:00,041 --> 00:44:04,471
♪Rise like tides that never fall♪

886
00:44:05,371 --> 00:44:07,551
♪If we're caught in a pouring rain♪

887
00:44:07,551 --> 00:44:08,641
♪That's alright♪

888
00:44:09,181 --> 00:44:09,931
♪If we're buried♪

889
00:44:09,931 --> 00:44:12,631
♪By passing years all the better♪

890
00:44:12,891 --> 00:44:15,071
♪At least we still can keep♪

891
00:44:15,251 --> 00:44:19,671
♪This one eternal photograph♪

892
00:44:35,431 --> 00:44:37,721
♪We're on misaligned tracks♪

893
00:44:37,721 --> 00:44:39,481
♪Running in opposite ways♪

894
00:44:39,601 --> 00:44:42,071
♪Searching all along the way♪

895
00:44:42,871 --> 00:44:45,031
♪For the fire of our younger hearts♪

896
00:44:45,221 --> 00:44:50,131
♪And the beauty lost in time♪

897
00:44:50,131 --> 00:44:53,651
♪This time don't lose each other again♪

898
00:44:53,891 --> 00:44:54,861
♪Only after loss♪

899
00:44:54,861 --> 00:44:57,491
♪Do we learn what truly matters most♪

900
00:44:57,901 --> 00:45:00,261
♪In another time and space♪

901
00:45:00,261 --> 00:45:01,821
♪We'll stay and walk together♪

902
00:45:01,821 --> 00:45:04,651
♪Till we grow old♪

903
00:45:05,611 --> 00:45:07,901
♪But still the sky will never♪

904
00:45:07,901 --> 00:45:10,571
♪Turn with the sea♪

905
00:45:13,091 --> 00:45:15,501
♪But still a swimming fish won't♪

906
00:45:15,501 --> 00:45:20,711
♪Fall in love with a flying bird♪
